00:39:18.446 --> 00:39:19.046 A:middle
And, creating a

00:39:19.046 --> 00:39:20.406 A:middle
dailyRoutineRelevanceProvider is

00:39:20.406 --> 00:39:20.956 A:middle
really easy.

00:39:20.956 --> 00:39:22.436 A:middle
You've just got to specify which

00:39:22.436 --> 00:39:23.566 A:middle
